'''2021年4月保加利亞議會選舉'''（{{lang-bg|Парламентарните избори в България през 2021 година}}）於2021年4月4日（星期日）舉行，選舉新一屆[[保加利亚|保加利亚]][[国民议会_(保加利亚)|國民議會]]的全數240位議員。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.dw.com/en/rise-up-and-democratic-bulgaria-seek-to-unseat-gerb/a-57066815|title=Rise Up and Democratic Bulgaria seek to unseat GERB|publisher=DW|date=2021-04-03|accessdate=2021-04-04|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513150638/https://www.dw.com/en/rise-up-and-democratic-bulgaria-seek-to-unseat-gerb/a-57066815|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==選舉制度==
[[国民议会_(保加利亚)|國民議會]]的240席由31個多議席選區以[[開放名單|開放名單]][[比例代表制|比例代表制]]產生。每個選區有4至16席不等。取得席位的全國[[选举门槛|得票率門檻]]為4%。無黨籍候選人需滿足[[最大餘額法|最大餘額法]]下的選舉配額（選區內有效票總數除以議席數）方可獲得席位。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Elections: Bulgaria Parliament 2014|url=https://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/2800/|accessdate=2021-04-08|language=en|publisher=IFES Election Guide|archive-date=2021-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210503013323/https://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/2800/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=coe01>{{Cite web |title=Observation of the parliamentary elections in Bulgaria (4 April 2021) |url=https://assembly.coe.int/nw/xml/XRef/Xref-XML2HTML-en.asp?fileid=29205&lang=en |date=2021-05-19 |website=assembly.coe.int |access-date=2021-11-15 |archive-date=2021-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211115102924/https://assembly.coe.int/nw/xml/XRef/Xref-XML2HTML-en.asp?fileid=29205&lang=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>

大約12,000個投票站於投票日早上7時至晚上8時開放。約670萬人有權投票。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.dw.com/en/bulgaria-heads-to-the-polls-amid-covid-discontent/a-57095992|title=Bulgaria heads to the polls amid COVID discontent|publisher=DW|date=2021-04-04|language=en|accessdate=2021-04-04|archive-date=2021-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404065154/https://www.dw.com/en/bulgaria-heads-to-the-polls-amid-covid-discontent/a-57095992|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==参选政党==
在{{le|绿党 (保加利亚)|The Greens (Bulgaria)|绿党}}2020年全国会议期间，该党代表投票赞成在“下一次议会选举中与{{le|民主保加利亚|Democratic Bulgaria}}的另外两个成员组成联盟”，投票反对“与当前国民议会中的任何政党组成联盟”，即[[保加利亚欧洲发展公民党|保加利亚欧洲发展公民党]]（GERB）、[[保加利亚社会党|保加利亚社会党]]（BSP）、[[争取权利和自由运动|争取权利和自由运动]]（DPS）、{{le|沃利亚运动|Volya Movement}}（Volya）和{{le|联合爱国者|United Patriots}}（OP）。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Владислав Панев и Борислав Сандов бяха преизбрани за съпредседатели на „Зелено движение“|url=https://www.zelenite.bg/18663|accessdate=2021-04-05|date=2020-09-28|work=The Greens|language=bg|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024165523/https://www.zelenite.bg/18663|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

{{le|有这样一个民族|There Is Such A People}}（ITN）副主席{{link-bg|托什科·约达诺夫|Тошко Йорданов}}在接受{{le|保加利亚国家电台|Bulgarian National Radio}}采访时说，该党“不会与GERB、DPS或BSP结成联盟”。<ref>{{Cite web|title=За партията на Слави Трифонов са забранени съюзи с ГЕРБ, БСП и ДПС|url=https://offnews.bg/politika/za-partiata-na-slavi-trifonov-sa-zabraneni-saiuzi-s-gerb-bsp-i-dps-737689.html|accessdate=2021-04-05|date=2020-10-07|work=OFF News|language=bg|archive-date=2020-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104210131/https://offnews.bg/politika/za-partiata-na-slavi-trifonov-sa-zabraneni-saiuzi-s-gerb-bsp-i-dps-737689.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

民主保加利亚的联合主席{{le|赫里斯托·伊万诺夫|Hristo Ivanov (politician)}}在接受[[bTV_(保加利亚)|bTV]]采访时表示，“无论有没有[[博伊科·鲍里索夫|鲍里索夫]]，都不会与GERB结盟”。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Христо Иванов: Коалиция с ГЕРБ няма да има със или без Борисов|url=https://offnews.bg/politika/hristo-ivanov-koalitcia-sas-gerb-niama-da-ima-sas-ili-bez-borisov-737955.html|accessdate=2021-04-05|date=2020-10-11|work=OFF News|language=bg|archive-date=2021-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211208122015/https://offnews.bg//politika/hristo-ivanov-koalitcia-s-gerb-niama-da-ima-sas-ili-bez-borisov-737955.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

{{le|保加利亚公民运动|Bulgaria for Citizens Movement}}主席迪米塔尔·德尔切夫（{{lang|bg|Димитър Делчев}}）在2020年8月{{le|斯拉维科夫广场|Slaveykov Square}}举行的公民讲台公开演讲中宣布，他的政党将加入{{le|起来保加利亚|Stand Up.BG}}<ref>{{Cite web|title=Димитър Делчев: Можем и имаме силите да изгоним грабливите животни от властническото гнездо|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wO8DM6rPMsQ|accessdate=2021-04-05|author=Изправи се.БГ|date=2020-08-31|work=YouTube|language=bg|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107020209/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wO8DM6rPMsQ|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|Volt欧洲|Volt Europa}}保加利亚分部主席纳斯蒂米尔·阿纳尼耶夫（{{lang|bg|Настимир Ананиев}}）<ref name="ytb">{{Cite web|title=НАСТИМИР АНАНИЕВ: ВЛАСТТА СЕ ПРОВАЛИ И НЕ ИЗПЪЛНИ ОЧАКВАНИЯТА НА СУВЕРЕНА|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DF1wKWbcmTM|accessdate=2021-04-05|author=Изправи се.БГ|date=2020-09-01|work=YouTube|language=bg|archive-date=2020-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018021010/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DF1wKWbcmTM|dead-url=no}}</ref>和{{le|运动21|Movement 21}}主席{{le|塔蒂亚娜·唐切娃|Tatyana Doncheva}}<ref>{{Cite web|title=Татяна Дончева и Движение 21 се присъединяват към мрежата Изправи се.БГ|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DF1wKWbcmTM|accessdate=2021-04-05|author=Изправи се.БГ|date=2020-08-31|work=YouTube|language=bg|archive-date=2020-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018021010/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DF1wKWbcmTM|dead-url=no}}</ref>也采取了同样的行动。公民团体{{le|这个系统杀了我们|The System Kills Us}}宣布支持尼古拉·瓦普萨罗夫（{{lang|bg|Никола Вапцаров}}）作为他们在{{le|起来保加利亚|Stand Up.BG}}的代表<ref name="ytb" />。

